snippet.title: Paladins Strike - Launch Trailer -  Available Now!
snippet.description: Paladins Strike is a 5v5 real-time multiplayer hero shooter, perfected for mobile. Players can master a diverse cast of more than 20 Champions with high-powered weapons and magical abilities. Now available globally on iOS and Android!
